    12_HW-Loop-Temp-Schedule,!- Name
    Temperature,             !- Schedule Type Limits Name
    Through: 12/31,          !- Field 1
    For: AllDays,            !- Field 2
    Until: 24:00, 82.2;      !- Field 4

